Package org.apache.wayang.spark.monitoring.interfaces

Interface Stage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StageCompleted, StageExecutorMetrics, StageSubmitted
    public interface Stage
extends java.io.Serializable
    This interface represents a stage in a data processing pipeline. A stage is a set of tasks that are executed together as part of a larger computation.
